# About Smart Virtualization

## Project Overview
This Android application prototype explores the concept of mobile virtualization, allowing devices to share computational resources over a network connection.

## Technical Details

### Architecture
- Client-Server model
- Resource monitoring system
- Virtual environment manager
- Network communication layer

### Implementation
- Built using Android Studio
- Java-based implementation
- Network protocols for device communication
- System resource management APIs

### Development Status
This is a prototype version demonstrating core concepts of:
- Resource sharing between devices
- Virtual environment creation
- Basic resource monitoring
- Network connectivity

## Development Timeline
- Initial Prototype: November 2024
- Basic functionality implementation
- UI/UX design
- Resource monitoring system

